text = "Your companion looks up from her book and her nest of picnic-goods. Her blanket is much softer than yours, and her spread of treats much more robust.

[BALDOMERA]: Are you unhappy, Betty?

[YOU]: I only think that things could be different. If he weren't in charge. If people didn't [i]want[/i] him in charge.

[BALDOMERA]: And yet you are here, never aging, eating snacks delivered by faithful adepts across the globe. Nobody likes rules, but I rather think you're coming out on top, wouldn't you say?"
